Today, my plan is to continue
the discussion of the two

00:00:34.045 --> 00:00:38.100
string system, which we were
working really hard last time

00:00:38.100 --> 00:00:40.210
but we sort of run out of time.

00:00:40.210 --> 00:00:43.830
So we didn't have time to
