doesn't surprise you--
will look like this,

01:11:16.600 --> 01:11:18.830
et cetera, et cetera.

01:11:18.830 --> 01:11:22.330
If I plot psi--

01:11:22.330 --> 01:11:25.810
if I plot psi as
a function of x.

01:11:31.120 --> 01:11:35.110
On the other hand, we
also know that psi P

01:11:35.110 --> 01:11:41.950
is proportional to d psi
partial psi partial x.

01:11:41.950 --> 01:11:50.370
Therefore, you can also plot
