01:12:01.870 --> 01:12:03.640
because it's got the wall.

01:12:03.640 --> 01:12:06.980
Therefore, it can
actually produce pressure

01:12:06.980 --> 01:12:08.080
on top of the wall.

01:12:08.080 --> 01:12:13.090
But you cannot move the position
of all of those molecules

01:12:13.090 --> 01:12:14.650
in front of the wall.

01:12:14.650 --> 01:12:16.230
Therefore, that makes sense.

01:12:16.230 --> 01:12:20.110
You will see exactly in
