01:12:32.800 --> 01:12:35.920
And basically, what you are
going to get is something like.

01:12:35.920 --> 01:12:39.880
The second normal mode,
et cetera, et cetera.

01:12:39.880 --> 01:12:46.930
So be careful about the
matching between the boundary

01:12:46.930 --> 01:12:53.020
condition obtained from the
