01:12:53.020 --> 01:12:54.430
They are identical.

01:12:54.430 --> 01:12:56.830
Open corresponds
responds to open,

01:12:56.830 --> 01:13:00.160
closed corresponds to
closed when you express

01:13:00.160 --> 01:13:04.060
your equation of
motion in terms of psi.

01:13:04.060 --> 01:13:07.390
On the other hand, if
